net.adamcin.oakpal.core

Class NamespaceMappingRequest.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.adamcin.oakpal.core.NamespaceMappingRequest.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    NamespaceMappingRequest

    public static final class NamespaceMappingRequest.Builder
extends Object
    Build a NamespaceMappingRequest by specifying which namespace mappings (by prefix or by uri) should be retained. Builtin namespace mappings are not retained by default, because they are added back in when converting a list of JcrNs mappings to a NamespaceMapping using JsonCnd.toNamespaceMapping(List).
